data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled in the heart of a quiet, welcoming New Braunfels neighborhood. This beautiful residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and tranquility. With its prime location near the Creekside Shopping Center and easy access to both I-35 and I-10 in Seguin, this property is a true gem waiting for you to make it your own. This home has an open floorplan kitchen, breakfast area and living room to maximize the space. For those who need the extra space, you will sure appreciate having a three car garage. Perhaps the most amazing thing about this home is that it has an assumable mortgage loan at 2.75% !!!
